### Variables
@productId = 66282daa-8032-41f7-9470-2f4321b41c47

### Create Product Review
# Note: Run auth.http login/register first to set the token variable
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "rating": 5,
  "title": "Отличный товар!",
  "body": "Очень доволен покупкой. Качество на высшем уровне, доставка быстрая. Рекомендую!"
}

### Create Product Review (Negative)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "product_id": "{{productId}}",
  "rating": 2,
  "title": "Не оправдал ожиданий",
  "body": "Качество товара оставляет желать лучшего. Не соответствует описанию."
}

### Get Product Reviews by Product ID (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/by_product/{{productId}}?page=1&page_size=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Product Reviews by Product ID (without pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/by_product/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Product Reviews by Product ID (page 2)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/product_review/by_product/{{productId}}?page=2&page_size=20
Content-Type: application/json
